{
  "stem": "12438.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Couldn't go out, couldn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just depend on faith.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whatever will happen, will happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And during the day it wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But at night, we were afraid to go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even you were afraid to be in the house, because most of the time the Nazis broken in the houses at night and took out the Jews.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And mostly they took out men members.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very-- very dangerous for men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From one house that I know, they took out the son and the father, the oldest son and the father at night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they never came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As, you know, women were not so afraid like men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Because I was going around with the English visa, and I couldn't leave.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So one day I was walking in the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I always had my passport with me, because we were afraid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I-- I really don't know what makes me think to go to the Italian embassy, ask for a visa.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember why I did it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I just went-- went into the consulate, they opened the door, an old man-- a very good looking, you know, a fine looking man with a goatee-- came out and asked me what I want.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I said-- I showed him the passport, and I said I would like to go to Italy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I cannot go to England.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Maybe from Italy I may be able to go to England.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He took the passport from me and he went into the other room and came out with a visa for six months.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Well, I went home and then right away I went to the synagogue there, to the-- the organization.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
